  "body": [
    "Treasury added four entities to the Iranian-shipping designation list overnight. The U.S. Department of State characterised the move as 'maintenance' of the existing framework; the agents read the same move as a meaningful expansion, because three of the four entities operate vessels in non-Iranian flags of convenience.",
    "Tanker AIS shows two re-routings in the last twelve hours that the desk classifies as precautionary, not crisis-driven. WTI is up 2.1% on the day; Brent crack spreads have not moved commensurately, which the agents read as the equity vol market under-pricing the chain.",
    "Tehran's response so far is rhetorical. The closure-event posterior at 30 days remains low (0.22 ± 0.07). The desk is publishing both the calm and the divergence."
